{"tid":687373,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(重開)老老實實,lebron james係咪二十世紀以來最有個性既球員?","createTime":"2018-06-02T08:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T12:35:09.000Z","uid":148749,"like":40,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"26fe722d3a6a5027a2575d5fcd9a955b737860b5","tid":687373,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:11:10.000Z","msg":"原貼<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/579607/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/579607/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n數口差:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e9BqUBYaHlM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3De9BqUBYaHlM&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b7efccef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e9BqUBYaHlM</a><br />\nlbj:我要為heat嬴得唔止2個,3個,4個,5個,6個,7個<br />\n結果2冠,拎埋亞冠都湊唔夠數<br />\n<br />\n調皮:<br />\n<a href=\"http://bleacherreport.com/articles/1637791-lebron-james-responds-to-flopping-allegations-not-one-of-those-guys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbleacherreport.com%2Farticles%2F1637791-lebron-james-responds-to-flopping-allegations-not-one-of-those-guys&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=ffa9e2d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://bleacherreport.com/articles/1637791-lebron-james-responds-to-flopping-allegations-not-one-of-those-guys</a><br />\nlbj:我唔需要假摔,我打既係aggressive既籃球<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=LeBron+James+flop+\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fresults%3Fsearch_query%3DLeBron%2BJames%2Bflop%2B&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=4bab146f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=LeBron+James+flop+</a><br />\n係utube一搵成咋都係<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dSdJQ-aXS-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdSdJQ-aXS-A&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=36e64585\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dSdJQ-aXS-A</a><br />\n對住自己隊友都要摔<br />\n<br />\n敬老:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.espn.com/nba/news/story?id=4650907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.espn.com%2Fnba%2Fnews%2Fstory%3Fid%3D4650907&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=6a89c239\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.espn.com/nba/news/story?id=4650907</a><br />\nlbj認為所以背號23既球員都應該選過另一個no. 以表示對mj既尊重<br />\n由佢開始<br />\n<br />\n念舊:<br />\n<a href=\"http://ftw.usatoday.com/2014/07/lebron-james-number-23\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fftw.usatoday.com%2F2014%2F07%2Flebron-james-number-23&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=623e8c20\" target=\"_blank\">http://ftw.usatoday.com/2014/07/lebron-james-number-23</a><br />\nlbj:2乘3=6,所以我選擇23號<br />\n而6號正正是當年在lbj騎士時的背號!<br />\n<br />\n跨欄:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CF52TQrYanw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCF52TQrYanw&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b880a53e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CF52TQrYanw</a><br />\n打波不忘跨欄<br />\n<br />\n為人設想:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FxfSnvh67SE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFxfSnvh67SE&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=5fbe19f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FxfSnvh67SE</a><br />\n唔想球童咁辛苦幫佢拎衫 直接扔落地<br />\n但係球童都係唔領情<br />\n<br />\n堅韌不屈:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.slamonline.com/nba/lebron-james-dont-believe-played-superteam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.slamonline.com%2Fnba%2Flebron-james-dont-believe-played-superteam%2F&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=50c2906b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.slamonline.com/nba/lebron-james-dont-believe-played-superteam/</a><br />\nlbj:我唔認為我有為超級強隊效力過<br />\n可見lbj拖住dwade,bosh,love,irving,raygun呢堆辣殺都可以三冠<br />\n証明lbj堅韌不屈既精神<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LoOXKha7uL4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLoOXKha7uL4&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=fdef4e8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LoOXKha7uL4</a><br />\n模仿慾:<br />\n同wade一似扮dirk咳<br />\n結果好似連病態都扮埋 單場8分比人4:2收皮<br />\n<br />\n直腸直肚:<br />\n<a href=\"https://uproxx.com/sports/report-lebron-james-hated-cleveland-nba-miami-heat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuproxx.com%2Fsports%2Freport-lebron-james-hated-cleveland-nba-miami-heat%2F&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d98ef85f\" target=\"_blank\">https://uproxx.com/sports/report-lebron-james-hated-cleveland-nba-miami-heat/</a><br />\nlbj:It&rsquo;s not far, but it is far. And Clevelanders, because they were the bigger-city kids when we were growing up, looked down on us.&hellip; So we didn&rsquo;t actually like Cleveland. We hated Cleveland growing up. There&rsquo;s a lot of people in Cleveland we still hate to this day.<br />\n懶得翻譯 內容大意係話自己唔鍾意克里夫蘭<br />\n<br />\n訓練營俾個細路顏樽段片都俾佢block埋<br />\n顏樽片:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2OO-3XHyXKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2OO-3XHyXKs&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=ab83d0cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2OO-3XHyXKs</a><br />\nblock片:<a href=\"http://bleacherreport.com/articles/214316-kings-edict-james-gets-dunked-on-by-college-player-confiscates-video\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbleacherreport.com%2Farticles%2F214316-kings-edict-james-gets-dunked-on-by-college-player-confiscates-video&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=42381319\" target=\"_blank\">http://bleacherreport.com/articles/214316-kings-edict-james-gets-dunked-on-by-college-player-confiscates-video</a><br />\n<br />\n親民:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qeg-wkmjtTQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dqeg-wkmjtTQ&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=60bad31f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qeg-wkmjtTQ</a><br />\n有碌小鳩 唔會令普通人覺得自己同nba球員差距甚大<br />\n<br />\n感性:<br />\n<a href=\"http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2645742\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbleacherreport.com%2Farticles%2F2645742&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=ba1e6dec\" target=\"_blank\">http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2645742</a><br />\n解釋自己跨過green因為後者叫佢bitch<br />\n傷害左佢既feeling<br />\n<br />\n自己選擇既路 走多幾步都要走完:<br />\n生涯代表作:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lhbM6uuCt74\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlhbM6uuCt74&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=0f2c7c45\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lhbM6uuCt74</a><br />\nplayoff走步絕殺wizards<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場加映 fuck off門:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=19322819&amp;extra=&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D19322819%26extra%3D%26page%3D1&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=4c9b0c66\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=19322819&amp;extra=&amp;page=1</a>(搵唔到原貼)<br />\n當年有版友自稱係james死忠<br />\n係james去 馬膠果陣 撞到佢 叫佢簽名<br />\njames同佢講左句 fuck off<br />\n之後個版友周圍唱<br />\n就咁咪foj囉"},{"pid":"0cbc6e88f6a643eacd0347882ef85785aef3eaa2","tid":687373,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:18:29.000Z","msg":"死番上去"},{"pid":"f233b7981b7789cd0b7a2a45933c74197c65474c","tid":687373,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"